data.name: MetroLabel1.Text
data.value: To continue this operation you must authorize Metro Image Uploader for the Cloud to access to your Dropbox account, We opened a Web browser for you with the authorization link. If it didn't open, click in "Copy Auth Link to the Clipboard" button and paste it in your favourite Web browser. After authorizing the app, click in the "Continue" button.

data.name: MetroLabel2.Text
data.value: To continue this operation you must authorize Metro Image Uploader for the Cloud to access to your Twitter account, We opened a Web browser for you with the authorization link. After authorizing the app, type your Twitter PIN in the text box and press Continue.
